      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_2222-2301",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2222-2301",
      "markText": "初二日 饭后，雨始止。遂越潦[1]攀岭，溪石渐幽。二十里，暮抵天封寺[2]。卧念晨上峰顶，以朗霁为缘，盖连日晚霁，并无晓晴。及五更梦中，闻明星满天，喜不成寐。",
      "totalCount": 527,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2222&rangeEnd=2301",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2222&rangeEnd=2301"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_538-553",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "538-553",
      "markText": "云散日朗，人意山光，俱有喜态。",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=538&rangeEnd=553",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=538&rangeEnd=553"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_2-89",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2-89",
      "markText": "天台山，又称“台山”，在今浙江天台县北，有华顶、赤城、琼台等名景，其中以石梁飞瀑最为著名。天台山为佛教天台宗的发祥地，有隋朝创建的国清寺。台州府省称“台郡”，即今浙江临海市。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=89",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=89"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_2486-2519",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2486-2519",
      "markText": "五更时从梦中醒来，听仆人说，满天都是明亮的星星，欢喜得无法再入睡。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2486&rangeEnd=2519",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2486&rangeEnd=2519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_1187-1202",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1187-1202",
      "markText": "翠丛中山鹃映发，今人攀历忘苦。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1187&rangeEnd=1202",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1187&rangeEnd=1202"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_2_572-590",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "572-590",
      "markText": "望雁山诸峰，芙蓉插天，片片扑人眉宇。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=572&rangeEnd=590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=572&rangeEnd=590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_418-440",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "418-440",
      "markText": "岭角山花盛开，顶上反不吐色，盖为高寒所勒耳。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=418&rangeEnd=440",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=418&rangeEnd=440"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_1_3120-3147",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "3120-3147",
      "markText": "山脚下山花盛开，峰顶上反而不开花，大概是高处寒冷所致。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=3120&rangeEnd=3147",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=3120&rangeEnd=3147"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_3_2185-2201",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2185-2201",
      "markText": "初四日 整天枯坐着听下雪的声音。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2185&rangeEnd=2201",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2185&rangeEnd=2201"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "37095832_2_3887-3905",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "3887-3905",
      "markText": "余见四山云雨凄凄，不能不为明晨忧也。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=37095832&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3887&rangeEnd=3905",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/aa23287072360998aa26999?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3887&rangeEnd=3905"
    },
